				"id": "ALAS2POSTGRESQL12-2024-012",
				"title": "Amazon Linux 2 - Postgresql12 2.0 - ALAS2POSTGRESQL12-2024-012: important priority package update for libpq",
				"description": "Package updates are available for Amazon Linux 2 - Postgresql12 that fix the following vulnerabilities:\nCVE-2024-7348:\n\tTime-of-check Time-of-use (TOCTOU) race condition in pg_dump in PostgreSQL allows an object creator to execute arbitrary SQL functions as the user running pg_dump, which is often a superuser. The attack involves replacing another relation type with a view or foreign table. The attack requires waiting for pg_dump to start, but winning the race condition is trivial if the attacker retains an open transaction. Versions before PostgreSQL 16.4, 15.8, 14.13, 13.16, and 12.20 are affected.\n",
